{{define "title"}}Weddings{{end}}

{{define "main"}}
    <main class="about" id="weddings">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="about-text">
            <h2>Weddings</h2>
            <div class="weddings">
                <strong>Planning your big day? We’re here to make it extra sweet</h3>

                <h3>How to Order a Wedding Cake</h3>
                <p>To get started, please send us a direct message with:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your wedding date</li>
                        <li>How many guests you'd like to serve</li>
                        <li>Any inspiration photos or theme ideas you have</li>
                    </ul>
                    <span>We’ll guide you through design options, size recommendations, and pricing tailored to your celebration.</span>
                </p>
                <br>

                <strong>Tasting Kit</strong>
                <p>We offer a <strong>Cake Sampling Kit</strong> for $35, which includes 4 flavours of your choice.
                    If you decide to order your wedding cake with us (minimum order of $300), the $35 will be deducted from your final cake price.

                    Want to try more than 4 flavours? No problem! Additional flavours can be added for <strong>$5 each</strong>.
                    Please note: the cost of extra flavours will not go towards your final cake price.
                </p>
                <br>

                <h3>Cake Sizes & Starting Prices</h3>
                <span>We offer a variety of sizes to suit weddings both intimate and grand:</span>>
                <p>
                    <ul><strong>Two-Tier Cakes</strong> 
                        <li><strong>4” top + 6” bottom</strong> – Serves 15–20 people — <em>Starts at $200 (simple design)</em></li>
                        <li><strong>6” top + 8” bottom</strong> – Serves 25–30 people — <em>Starts at $250</em></li>
                        <li><strong>8” top + 10” bottom</strong> – Serves 35–45 people — <em>Starts at $300</em></li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul><strong>Three-Tier Cakes</strong> 
                        <li><strong>4” + 6” + 8”</strong> – Serves 40–50 people — <em>Starts at $350 (simple design)</em></li>
                        <li><strong>6” + 8” + 10”</strong> – Serves 60–70 people — <em>Starts at $400</em></li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <span>For larger weddings or custom sizes, please contact us directly for a quote.</span>
                <br>
                <h3>Delivery</h3>
                <p>We offer delivery for wedding cakes with <strong>two tiers and up</strong>.
                    <ul>
                        <li>Minimum order for delivery: $250</li>
                        <li>Delivery fee: $40</li>
                    </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
{{end}}